    "Record IDs format: PRSN-YYMMDD-NNNN (people), CMPY-YYMMDD-NNNN (companies)",
    "One-to-one-to-one mapping enforced (1 Email = 1 WP User = 1 Record ID)",
    "No errors in production logs",
    "Health check passes (all 18+ checks)"
  ],
